itl.enabler.api

Interface PumpCollection.PumpCollectionEventListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.EventListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PumpCollection.PumpCollectionEventAdapter
    Enclosing class:
    PumpCollection

    public static interface PumpCollection.PumpCollectionEventListener
extends java.util.EventListener
    Listens to events from every Pump in the collection.
    Clients can either implement this interface to receive events on the whole Pump Collection or subscribe to events from individual pumpsByNum.
    See Also:
    Pump.PumpEventListener
